## Spacing & shape

| Token | CSS variable | Default | Usage |
| ----- | ------------ | ------- | ----- |
| Panel radius | `--orbit-radius` | `1.25rem` | Large panels |
| Card radius | `--orbit-card-radius` | `1rem` | Game cards |
| Blur | `--orbit-blur` | `24px` | Glass backdrop |
| Motion duration | `--orbit-motion-duration` | `0.35s` | Transitions |
| Motion easing | `--orbit-motion-easing` | cubic-bezier | Screen + theme transitions |

